dct_title_s: Map of the North Island of New Zealand including the provinces of Auckland, Taranaki, Hawke's Bay, and Wellington with all the recent surveys
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
In upper margin: To face page 126. 0.59--Return--New Zealand.
Publisher's no. from its catalog of nineteenth century maps of New Zealand from the British Parliamentary papers: 52.
Includes inset of "Middle Island" and statistical table of confiscated lands.
